status.description:
Status codes
0 = Unpaid
1 = Overdue
2 = Fully paid
3 = Partially paid
4 = Overpaid
5 = Deleted
6 = Customer loss
7 = Marked for collection
8 = Sent for collection
40 = ROT/RUT Awaiting customer payment
41 = ROT/RUT Ready to send application
42 = ROT/RUT Application sent
43 = ROT/RUT Deleted
100 = Invoier initiated
101 = Invoier pending
102 = Invoier sold
103 = Invoier paid
104 = Invoier rejected
105 = Invoier awaiting
106 = Invoier approved
107 = Invoier payment_underway
1102 = E-invoice pending
1200 = E-invoice success
1500 = E-invoice failed
